cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper presents a method for compressing deep neural networks, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The method involves quantization and compression, which are also relevant to multimedia (cs.MM). The paper uses a rate-distortion function to minimize the impact of quantization on accuracy, which is a common approach in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
